&lt;p&gt;The General Surgery Team in Glangwili General Hospital is currently recruiting an enthusiastic, forward thinking Physician Associate, to work within our department. The role provides a great opportunity to join a committed team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for talented individuals to become a member of our quality care delivery team who are highly motivated with excellent communication, leadership and team building skills. In joining the Surgical department the successful candidate will be joining a friendly and supportive team of clinical, nursing and admin staff working closely alongside highly skilled team of allied health care professionals.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The ability to speak Welsh is desirable for this post; English and/or Welsh speakers are equally welcome to apply&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;NameBethan PerkinsJob titleService ManagerEmail addressbethan.perkins2@wales.nhs.ukTelephone number01554 899011&lt;/p&gt;
